doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    title Monthly Content Calendar
    style.
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        border: 0;
        border-spacing: 0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        color: #333;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      td {
        padding: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header {
        padding: 20px 40px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px 40px;
      }
      p{
        font-size: 18px;
        margin: 0;
        text-align : left;
      }
      .data-table{
        width: 100%; 
        border-radius: 12px;
      }
      .data-table th, .data-table td {
        padding: 16px;
      }
      .data-table th{
        border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
        
      }
      .data-table td{
        border-bottom: 1px solid #E4E4E4;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
  body
    table(role='presentation', style='background-color: #ffffff; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;')
      thead
        tr
          td.header
            img(src='https://i.imgur.com/SgaAwWy.png', alt='Agent Automated logo' height='100' width='150')
        tr
          td.header(style='text-align: left')  
            h2 Your upcoming months posts!
      tbody 
        tr 
          td(style='text-align: left; padding: 0 40px') Hi Nicola,
        tr 
          td.content
            p Find a calendar with your automated posting schedule for the month! As always, go to your account here to adjust times, captions, or anything else. We are thankful to serve you and your business and reach out with any comments or questions!
            br
            p Sicerely, The Agents Automated Team
        tr 
          td(style='padding: 20px 40px') 
            img(src=calendarImageUrl, alt='Monthly Content Calendar')
        tr 
          td(style='text-align: left; padding:80px')
            p We believe feedback is a gift! Do you have questions, comments or suggestions? Please reach out to colby@agentsautomated.com !
            br
            p -Sicerely, Colby, Founder of Agents Automated Team